    <item>
      <title>由于需求疲软，苹果 iPhone 在中国大幅打折</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/apple-s-iphone-steeply-discounted-in-china-on-weak-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司在中国的经销商将 iPhone 15 机型的价格下调了 180 美元，这表明需求持续低迷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/apple-s-iphone-steeply-discounted-in-china-on-weak-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 10:17:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度同意投资 150 亿美元的里程碑式芯片工厂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/india-approves-15-billion-in-milestone-chip-plant-investments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度政府已批准对半导体制造工厂进行价值 152 亿美元的投资，其中包括塔塔集团 (Tata Group) 建设印度首个大型芯片制造工厂的提案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/india-approves-15-billion-in-milestone-chip-plant-investments</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 10:11:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>跨国公司将土耳其数据法视为投资绿灯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/turkey-data-protection-law-reform-seen-as-green-light-for-investment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其将允许国际公司将当地客户的数据移出该国，这是一项期待已久的数据保护规则改革，企业称这可能会吸引数十亿美元的外国直接投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/turkey-data-protection-law-reform-seen-as-green-light-for-investment</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 09:22:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据说亿万富翁克雷廷斯基正在考虑重新收购 Atos</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/billionaire-kretinsky-is-said-to-weigh-renewed-bid-for-atos</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，亿万富翁丹尼尔·克雷廷斯基(Daniel Kretinsky)放弃了此前对这家陷入困境的法国IT公司旗下子公司的收购报价，目前正在考虑对Atos SE的部分业务重新提出收购要约。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/billionaire-kretinsky-is-said-to-weigh-renewed-bid-for-atos</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 09:17:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台积电任命两名退伍军人为首席运营官</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/tsmc-elevates-two-veterans-to-coo-in-succession-move</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台积电提拔两名高级管理人员分担首席运营官职责，预示着这家全球最大代工芯片制造商将迎来新一代领导者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/tsmc-elevates-two-veterans-to-coo-in-succession-move</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 08:55:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人工智能需求推动台湾今年 GDP 反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/taiwan-sees-economy-rebounding-this-year-fueled-by-ai-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾预计，随着全球对人工智能相关技术的需求激增，推动经济增长，台湾经济今年将从 2023 年的低迷状态中迅速反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/taiwan-sees-economy-rebounding-this-year-fueled-by-ai-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 08:45:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Ocado 预计仓库将在 4 亿英镑损失后实现增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/ocado-predicts-robot-warehouse-growth-after-400-million-loss</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Ocado Group Plc 去年亏损近 4 亿英镑（5.06 亿美元），但表示在推出自动化技术和与零售商合作方面正在取得进展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/ocado-predicts-robot-warehouse-growth-after-400-million-loss</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 07:52:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>C3.ai 任命新首席财务官，这是不到十年内第十位担任该职位的人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/c3-ai-gains-after-sales-forecast-signals-demand-for-ai-tools</link>
      <description><![CDATA[C3.ai Inc. 公布的销售数据表明客户对该软件公司基于人工智能的新应用程序做出了积极反应，该公司在盘前交易中上涨了 16%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/c3-ai-gains-after-sales-forecast-signals-demand-for-ai-tools</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 21:47:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Snowflake 的 Frank Slootman 将从首席执行官职位上退休，将继续担任董事会主席</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/snowflake-misses-estimates-says-ceo-slootman-to-step-down</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在软件制造商发布了令人失望的销售预测并宣布首席执行官 Frank Slootman 辞职后，Snowflake Inc. 正面临有记录以来的最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/snowflake-misses-estimates-says-ceo-slootman-to-step-down</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 21:12:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
